headline: Waymo customer swears off autonomous driving after close call
summary: Waymo has achieved impressive expansion this year. As of July 2025, Waymo One is available 24/7 to customers in Los Angeles, Phoenix, and the San Francisco Bay Area. Waymo partners with Uber in Austin and Atlanta. The company recently announced plans to expand into other cities ...
